channel.title: Best base for beginner
channel.description: Hey. I'm new to java coding, so I'd like to get started with some base to make my own release. Which base would be the best for me? :]

item.title: Best base for beginner
item.dc:creator: @NieX NieX
item.description:
@NieX wrote:

it’s all very opinionated. Some recommend Delta for starters? but tbh if you start on Delta and move up into PI you will find it strange, confusing and most likely out of all cases rather difficult. I can give you a hand with your programming (show you the basics). In conclusion i recommend you start with PI … I will probably get hate for this, but like i said, this is my opinion.

Skype: Xyphsta
